tasks.implementationGuide:
1. blog/app/layout.tsx의 기본 metadata에 openGraph 추가:
   - openGraph: { title, description, type: 'website', siteName: 'Dev Blog' }

2. blog/app/posts/[slug]/page.tsx의 generateMetadata()에 openGraph 추가:
   - openGraph: { title: post.title, description: `${post.category} | ${post.tags.join(', ')}`, type: 'article', publishedTime: post.publishedAt }

3. blog/app/category/[name]/page.tsx의 generateMetadata()에 openGraph 추가:
   - openGraph: { title: `${decodedName} 카테고리`, description: `${decodedName} 카테고리의 글 목록`, type: 'website' }
